12 Oct 2015 Liberia: Ecap Two program to benefit 1.5 million people
http://allafrica.com/stories/201510122985.html
[Funded by the U.S. Foreign Disaster Assistance (OFDA), Mercy Corps has launched a 2nd phase of its Ebola community action program (ECAP 2) in Gbarnga. The program targets a wide network of local non-governmental organizations (NGOs) and radio stations across Liberia to enhance community preparedness against Ebola virus disease (EVD) and other major infectious diseases

